Planned features, fixes and enhancements:

- More complete XQuery 1.1 support
 + General FLWOR (unrestricted order of expressions, outer for, count)
 + Group By (also continuous Group By)
 + external variable/context item extensions
 
- More complete Fulltext Support
 + For scoring
 + Weights
 
- Fine-grained, automatic store selection, 
- mixing updatable, fulltext and streaming stores within the same query/module
- Performance improvements (CPU/memory)

Platforms:
- Android

Packaging:
 - Streaming Server inside an application server,
 - Streaming Server inside an JBI-compatible ESB